<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Server Error</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #283c86 0%, #45a247 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 150px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fff, #c5e1a5);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .back-home {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .back-home:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .gears-container {
            position: relative;
            height: 160px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .gear {
            position: absolute;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .gear::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            width: 20%;
            height: 20%;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .gear-teeth {
            position: absolute;
            width: 20%;
            height: 10%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            transform-origin: 100% 50%;
        }

        .gear-1 {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            top: 20px;
            left: calc(50% - 150px);
            animation: rotate 10s linear infinite;
        }

        .gear-2 {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            top: 40px;
            left: calc(50% - 30px);
            animation: rotate 7s linear infinite reverse;
        }

        .gear-3 {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            top: 30px;
            left: calc(50% + 60px);
            animation: rotate 8s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }

            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        .cog-icon {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                opacity: 0.8;
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <i class="fas fa-tools maintenance-icon"></i>
        <div class="gears-container">
            <div class="gear gear-1">
                <i class="fas fa-cog cog-icon"></i>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(0deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(30deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(60deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(90deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(120deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(150deg)"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="gear gear-2">
                <i class="fas fa-cog cog-icon"></i>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(0deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(45deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(90deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(135deg)"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="gear gear-3">
                <i class="fas fa-cog cog-icon"></i>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(0deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(40deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(80deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(120deg)"></div>
                <div class="gear-teeth" style="transform: rotate(160deg)"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="error-code">500</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">Internal Server Error</h1>
        <p class="error-message">
            Oops! Something went wrong on our servers. Our technical team has been notified and is working to fix the
            issue.
        </p>
        <p class="error-message">
            Please try again later or contact support if the problem persists.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="back-home">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Return to Homepage
        </a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>